)"}], "title": "Video by thefilmessential", "description": "Robert Pattinson was reportedly offered the lead role but passed. Despite being one of the rare Canadian films to receive a wide release in both Canada and the US, it became a box office failure. Interestingly, it made more in its first week than Crimes of the Future did in its entire theatrical run, a film directed by Brandon Cronenberg's father, David Cronenberg.\n\nInfinity Pool (2023)", "duration": 10.048, "timestamp": 1770393796, "uploader_id": "65091463837", "uploader": "The Film Essential", "channel": "thefilmessential", "like_count": 50108, "comment_count": 177, "comments": [{"author": "jesus_h_chris", "author_id": "7217563257", "id": "18081638357568942", "text": "It wasnt a good movie, but that part was funny", "timestamp": 1775509259}, {"author": "sunna_gamak", "author_id": "80428603043", "id": "18149042308420308", "text": "😍какая она классная ,всё роли", "timestamp": 1775424929}, {"author": "dancr452", "author_id": "1610430714", "id": "18428425450138738", "text": "Had potential and then just bombed", "timestamp": 1775363178}, {"author": "spencie_riggs", "author_id": "1444160143", "id": "18008413262851896", "text": "Mia goth top 3 actresses of the past 10 years. I will die on that hill.", "timestamp": 1775052326}, {"author": "zeakauri", "author_id": "38916554", "id": "17990901860948541", "text": "One of the best horrors i’ve seen for years", "timestamp": 1775045456}, {"author": "victoriascrivner", "author_id": "79405949082", "id": "17848397457677750", "text": "She so odd and I love her", "timestamp": 1774996782}, {"author": "lxnenxte.flac", "author_id": "7622761499", "id": "18066950105328253", "text": "", "timestamp": 1774953715}, {"author": "yaliqueur", "author_id": "6080094629", "id": "18190377709363813", "text": "марго", "timestamp": 1774909929}, {"author": "newbie00100", "author_id": "1735703689", "id": "18042417962746732", "text": "I love her! I wish she knew she’s too good for Shia. Most ama